{"lemma":"زَلْزَلاتٌ","slug":"زَلْزَلاتٌ","root":"ز.ل.ز.ل","root_slug":"ز-ل-ز-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ز-ل-ز-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"زَلْزَلَة","root":"زلزل","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n17946","n17961"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B2%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%92%D8%B2%D9%8E%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of زَلْزَلَ (zalzala) (form Iq)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"shaking"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"earthquake, seism"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"calamities","tags":["in-plural"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/zal.za.la/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n17946","headword_ar":"زَلْزَلَهُ","root":"zl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, * Msb, K, &c.,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zalozalapN","text_ar":"زَلْزَلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zilozaAlN","text_ar":"زِلْزَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zalozaAlN","text_ar":"زَلْزَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zulozaAlN","text_ar":"زُلْزَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or the first of these is an inf. n. [by universal consent], (S,) and so is the second, but the third is a simple subst., (Zj, S, Msb,) though this and the fourth [which is the least known] have the authority of certain readings of passages of the Kur, namely, xcix. 1 for both of these, and xxxiii. 11 for the latter of them, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He put it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"him, into a state of motion, commotion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"agitation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"into a state of convulsion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"violent motion."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Zj, TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zalozala A@ll~`hu AlA^aroDa","text_ar":"زَلْزَلَ ا@للّٰهُ الاَرْضَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"God made the earth to quake:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to quake violently:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (S:) [or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"put the earth into a state of convulsion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"violent motion."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Zj, TA) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaA='a biAlA_ibili yuzaloziluhaA","text_ar":"جَا=ءَ بِالاـِبِلِ يُزَلْزِلُهَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He came with,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"brought, the camels, driving them with roughness, violence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vehemence."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) Some say that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zalozalapN","text_ar":"زَلْزَلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alz~alalu fiY Alr~aA^oYi","text_ar":"الزَّلَلُ فِى الرَّاْىِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. “ the making a slip in judgment, or opinion ”]: so when one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zulozila Alqawomu","text_ar":"زُلْزِلَ القَوْمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"the meaning is,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"party, were turned away from the right course, and fear was cast into their hearts."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) It is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aall~`hum~a","text_ar":"اَللّٰهُمَّ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A@hozimi AlA^aHozaAba wazalozilohumo","text_ar":"ا@هْزِمِ الاَحْزَابَ وَزَلْزِلْهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"O God, rout, defeat,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"put to flight, the combined forces, and"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"make their state of affairs to be unsound,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unsettled."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) Accord. to IAmb,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSaAbati Alqawoma zalozalapN","text_ar":"اَصَابَتِ القَوْمَ زَلْزَلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An affrighting befell the people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"party;"},{"kind":"text","text":"from the saying in the Kur [ii. 210],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wazuloziluwA Hat~aY yaquwla","text_ar":"وَزُلْزِلُوا حَتَّى يَقُولَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~asuwlu","text_ar":"الرَّسُولُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And they were affrighted"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so that the Apostle said"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (L, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"were vehemently agitated."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ksh, Bd.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA zalozalotu qaT~u maA='F A^aborada mino","text_ar":"مَا زَلْزَلْتُ قَطُّ مَا=ءً اَبْرَدَ مِنْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA='i Alvgwbi","text_ar":"مَا=ءِ الثغوبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alv~agabi","text_ar":"الثَّغَبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as it is written in the explanation of this saying, the latter being app. the right reading], said by Aboo-Shembel, means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I have not put into my throat,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fauces, ever, water slipping into it cooler than the water of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vagab","text_ar":"ثَغَب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pool left by a torrent in the shade of a mountain"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Az, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","S","Zj","Msb","TA","L"]},{"entry_id":"n17961","headword_ar":"زَلْزَلَةٌ","root":"zl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see what next follows."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}